modules.description: Provides functions to retrieve emoji byte sequences by name, category, or subcategory, and to list all emojis. Works with strings, byte sequences, and category identifiers. Used to filter emojis by type, such as retrieving all "Emoticons" or "Supplemental Symbols and Pictographs."

The module provides functions to generate UTF-8 encoded emoji strings, including variations with skin tone modifiers, flags, and thematic categories like gestures, objects, and symbolic icons. It operates on Unicode code points and emoji combinations, supporting use cases such as representing diverse human figures, cultural symbols, and contextual expressions with precise visual distinctions.
